            </div>
          </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Banner Section -->
    <div class="banner">
      <div class="banner-text-left">
        <h2>FALL WINTER 2024</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="banner-text-right">
        <h2>NEW COLLECTION</h2>
        <a href="#" class="shop-button">SHOP NOW</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
<!--Carousel-->
  <div id="howItWorksCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
    <h2 class="carousel-title">How it Works</h2>
    <div class="carousel-inner">
      <!-- Slide 1 -->
      <div class="carousel-item active">
        <div class="carousel-content">
          <img src="resources/images/theFabric.webp" class="carousel-image" alt="Step 1">
          <div class="carousel-text">
            <h3>Step 1</h3>
            <h4>The best of Made in VietNam</h4>
            <p>Choose your preferred fabric based on your style and the occasion.</p>
            <p>If you're unsure, create your bunch kit to touch and feel the fabrics, or visit us at our atelier.</p>
            <a href="#" class="get-started">GET STARTED</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Slide 2 -->
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <div class="carousel-content">
          <img src="resources/images/personalization.webp" class="carousel-image" alt="Step 2">
          <div class="carousel-text">
            <h3>Step 2</h3>
            <h4>Configure your unique piece</h4>
            <p>Choose all the details of your garment: from the model to lapels, cuffs,
              pockets, buttons, and much more.
            </p>
            <p>Our experts will guide you through the process for a precise and comfortable fit.</p>
            <a href="#" class="get-started">GET STARTED</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Slide 3 -->
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <div class="carousel-content">
          <img src="resources/images/measurement.webp" class="carousel-image" alt="Step 3">
          <div class="carousel-text">
            <h3>Step 3</h3>
            <h4>In atelier or online</h4>
            <p>Visit one of the N3Tailored to get your measurements taken: our
              Style Advisors will be happy to welcome and assist you in achieving the perfect fit.</p>
            <p>Or, watch our tutorial to input them independently.</p>
            <a href="#" class="get-started">GET STARTED</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- nút cho Carousel -->
    <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#howItWorksCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
      <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
    </button>
    <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#howItWorksCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
      <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
    </button>
